Source: possumwood
Section: graphics
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Martin Prazak <martin.prazak@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), cmake, libboost-all-dev, libcgal-dev, libqt5opengl5-dev, libglew-dev, libglu1-mesa-dev, libtbb-dev, libpthread-stubs0-dev, libopenimageio-dev, libopenexr-dev, libilmbase-dev, freeglut3-dev, libluabind-dev, libglfw3-dev, pkg-config, libopencv-dev, libmpfr-dev, libjsoncpp-dev, libeigen3-dev, libjemalloc-dev, nlohmann-json-dev | nlohmann-json3-dev
